			<section class="comment-content comment">
				<p>Never thought about putting the gutter in it&#8217;s own class. Much better idea than doing a &#8220;last&#8221; class that removes a built-in gutter.</p>
<p>If I might make a couple of suggestions, though. Name your col class something like .float-left, and your clear class to .clear-left.</p>
<p>This gives you the ability to use them in other places other than framework, and gives you a descriptive name so that you can remember what they were doing later on.</p>
